      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"251\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/22184234/activity.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1481810876460&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=130&amp;height=146\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/22184234/activity.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1481810876460&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"146\" data-width=\"130\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"22195910\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"activity.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"22184234\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"6\" data-media-id=\"0f9bc378-290f-482d-8b5f-23936cb92bd5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/22184234/activity.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1481810876460&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=130&amp;height=146 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/22184234/activity.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1481810876460&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=130&amp;height=146 1x\"></span><p /><p>The Blade Activity pane displays a quick visual summary of the health of the blades.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Blade Activity Summary</strong></p><p>The first section gives a quick numerical summary of the number of slots, number active, and number of unresponsive blades.<br/> </p></li><li><p><strong>Graphic Activity Meter</strong></p><p>A block is drawn for every blade (not every slot) in the farm. The block is color coded to show current status.</p><ul><li><p>Green - Active</p></li><li><p>Gray - Inactive</p></li><li><p>Dark Grey - Non-responsive (The blade has not checked in for at least 6 minutes)</p></li></ul><p>Hovering the mouse over a block will display the name of that blade and its current status. Clicking on the block will select the block in the <em>Blade List</em> pane and bring up full information in the <em>Blade Info</em> pane.</p></li></ul>"
    }
  },
